"{\"uid\": \"inews.co.uk-news-inside-paris-olympics-269m-security-operation-3177751\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMPARTIAL NEWS + INTELLIGENT DEBATE Account From a 'ring of steel' around the Seine to RAF anti-drone teams and Qatari armoured vehicles, a vast operation is under way With days to go before the opening ceremony ofParis 2024, residents and tourists alike this week got their first discomfiting taste of the extraordinary measures needed to make theOlympic Gamesa reality.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 80, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9573886090615595e-22, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 89, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Air_Force\", \"score\": 0.9960886575333038, \"rank\": 0.003926701079166434, \"text\": \"RAF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Air_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NEWS\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 14}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'ring\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 56}, {\"ngram\": \"steel\", \"from\": 60, \"to\": 65}, {\"ngram\": \"Qatari armoured vehicles\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 136}, {\"ngram\": \"a vast operation\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 167}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"their first discomfiting taste\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"the extraordinary measures\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the early hours of Thursday, a vast swathe of the French capital became the subject of a strict week-long security clampdown.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9969834902429977, \"rank\": 0.0025021586657926103, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early hours\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"a vast swathe\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 420}, {\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"a strict week-long security clampdown\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until next Saturday, anyone wishing to wander along the banks of the Seine river where thepioneering opening ceremonyis planned to take place on 26 July, or simply meander past glories from theEiffel TowertoNotre Dame, will need to produce a pre-authorised QR code and undergo a stringent search to pass through a security cordon.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 574, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9573886090615595e-22, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"next Saturday\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"opening ceremonyis\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"26 July\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"glories\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"theEiffel TowertoNotre Dame\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"a pre-authorised QR code\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"a stringent search\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"a security cordon\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All vehicles, with the exception of those belonging to the emergency services, will be more or less banned from the security zone.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All vehicles\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the exception\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the emergency services\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"the security zone\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians, not generally known for their forbearance of state interference in daily life at the best of times, are unimpressed.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"their forbearance\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"state interference\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"daily life\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The head of the body representing the Paris region hospitality industry complained volubly last week of a \\\"disastrous\\\" intervention which \\\"means you will have to show papers even to drink a coffee\\\".\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.075874275631171e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The head\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"disastrous\\\" intervention\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"papers\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"a coffee\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1292}]}, {\"sente