ing from Russian cyber attacks and disinformation campaigns through to the threat of strikes and protests amid the aftermath ofFrance's divisive electionswhich have pitched the country into political turmoil.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2584, \"end\": 2591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"score\": 0.8417579657650972, \"rank\": 0.18766132625258836, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Armed_Forces\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adevil's brew\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"other menacesto\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"disinformation campaigns\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"the threat\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"strikes\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"the aftermath ofFrance's divisive electionswhich\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"political turmoil\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the re-emergence in recent weeks and months of Islamist terrorism, most dauntingly in the shape of the Islamic State attack on aMoscow concert hallin March which left 145 dead, and a broader upsurge in geo-political violence - whether it be the Ukraine war, the Israeli bombardment of Gaza or even last week's assassination attempt onDonald Trump- has added to concern that the Olympics are a prime target for an atrocity.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_State\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9895372632354964e-21, \"text\": \"Islamic State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp