\"\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"theIslamic Stateterror group\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"an image\", \"from\": 3258, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"its followers\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"an armed drone\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3308}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3337}, {\"ngram\": \"a slogan\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"Lone wolves' Olympics\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To date, the French authorities have foiled what they said were at least three potential plots by lone individuals to attack the Games, including a Chechen teenager suspected of targeting an Olympics football game and an 18-year-old far-right extremist who was arrested by counter-terror officers on Wednesday after he made threats on a neo-Nazi social media chat group.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3403, \"end\": 3409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9969834902429977, \"rank\": 0.0025021586657926103, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3538, \"end\": 3545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechnya\", \"score\": 0.9987160692035004, \"rank\": 0.001283656733392424, \"text\": \"Chechen\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechnya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chechnya\"}, {\"begin\": 3727, \"end\": 3735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neo-Nazism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.031614414455341e-41, \"text\": \"neo-Nazi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neo-Nazism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neo-Nazism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"at least three potential plots\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3484}, {\"ngram\": \"lone individuals\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3504}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics football game\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3603}, {\"ngram\": \"an 18-year-old far-right extremist\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3642}, {\"ngram\": \"counter-terror officers\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3686}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3699}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One Western security official toldithis week: \\\"Anything which chips away at stability in Europe or America is right now a priority for a wide range of threat actors.\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One Western security official\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3791}, {\"ngram\": \"Anything\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3817}, {\"ngram\": \"stability\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3847}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3857}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3868}, {\"ngram\": \"a priority\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3892}, {\"ngram\": \"a wide range\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3909}, {\"ngram\": \"threat actors\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics is a prominent symbol in that regard and there are many, many groups out there - from extremists to nation states - who would really like to damage it.\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 4098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3932, \"end\": 3946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a prominent symbol\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3968}, {\"ngram\": \"that regard\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3983}, {\"ngram\": \"many, many groups\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4015}, {\"ngram\": \"extremists\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"nation states\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In order to protect [the Games], you need to mount the sort of security operation that has similar intensity to being on a war footing.\", \"from\": 4100, \"to\": 4236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4109}, {\"ngram\": \"[the Games\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"the sort\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"security operation\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"similar intensity\", \"from\": 4192, \"to\": 4209}, {\"ngram\": \"a war footing\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The threat is very real, but France has among the best security apparatus available.\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4266, \"end\": 4272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997052605007668, \"rank\": 0.0002179393856925317, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The threat\", \"from\": 4237, \"to\": 4247}, {\"ngram\": \"the best security apparatus\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will be ready.\\\"\", \"from\": 4322, \"to\": 4342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not a sentiment shared entirely, it would seem, by the French themselves.\", \"from\": 4344, \"to\": 4423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sentiment\", \"from\": 4354, \"to\": 4365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A survey published this week by Paris-based pollsters Odoxa found that 64 per cent of French people believe that security for the Games is \\\"uncertain\\\" and half would like to see the Seine procession, due to be attended by 300,000 spectators, abandoned in favour of a single-venue parade centred around the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4511, \"end\": 4524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 4607, \"end\": 4612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9573886090615595e-22, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A survey\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4433}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-based pollsters\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4478}, {\"ngram\": \"Odoxa\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4484}, {\"ngram\": \"64 per cent\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4507}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 4538, \"to\": 4546}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4560}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 4580, \"to\": 4584}, {\"ngram\": \"300,000 spectators\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4665}, {\"ngram\": \"favour\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"a single-venue parade\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4711}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 4727, \"to\": 4743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The places considered by the public to be most vulnerable to a terror attack over the next month are tourist attractions, the public transport network and Olympic fan zones.\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The places\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4755}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 4770, \"to\": 4780}, {\"ngram\": \"a terror attack\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4821}, {\"ngram\": \"the next month\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"tourist attractions\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4865}, {\"ngram\": \"the public transport network\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4895}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic fan zones\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 4917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, it is the sheer scale of the Olympics - the Paris Games will encompass 36 locations in France, plus the surfing competition in Tahiti - that makes it such a complex task to protect, with tight security around venues viewed as being likely to deflect any attackers towards softer targets.\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 5215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5015, \"end\": 5021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997052605007668, \"rank\": 0.0002179393856925317, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5055, \"end\": 5061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.999999805745593, \"rank\": 1.9425444972452774e-07, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sheer scale\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4949}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4953, \"to\": 4965}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 4983}, {\"ngram\": \"36 locations\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5011}, {\"ngram\": \"the surfing competition\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5051}, {\"ngram\": \"tight security\", \"from\": 5115, \"to\": 5129}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5143}, {\"ngram\": \"any attackers\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5191}, {\"ngram\": \"softer targets\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a recent briefing by S&P Global, a data and risk analysis giant, put it: \\\"The high level of security in place at and around the Olympic venues is likely to motivate individuals or small cells intent on conducting an attack during the Games to attempt to target other locations, including fan zones, queues outside of venues, hotels, restaurants and transport hubs.\\\"\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5241, \"end\": 5251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S&P_Global\", \"score\": 0.9973396763790415, \"rank\": 0.0026674198204987482, \"text\": \"S&P Global\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S&P_Global\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S&P_Global\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recent briefing\", \"from\": 5220, \"to\": 5237}, {\"ngram\": \"a data and risk analysis giant\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5283}, {\"ngram\": \"The high level\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5308}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5320}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5329}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic venues\", \"from\": 5344, \"to\": 5362}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5396}, {\"ngram\": \"small cells\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5411}, {\"ngram\": \"an attack\", \"from\": 5433, \"to\": 5442}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"other locations\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5496}, {\"ngram\": \"fan zones\", \"from\": 5508, \"to\": 5517}, {\"ngram\": \"queues\", \"from\": 5519, \"to\": 5525}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5543}, {\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 5545, \"to\": 5551}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5564}, {\"ngram\": \"transport hubs\", \"from\": 5569, \"to\": 5583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the near doubling of public transport fares to the irritations of needing a QR code to go for a walk along the Seine, the Paris Olympics is proving less than a hit with some Parisians and tourists alike.\", \"from\": 5587, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5703, \"end\": 5708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9573886090615595e-22, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the near doubling\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5609}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport fares\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5635}, {\"ngram\": \"the irritations\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5654}, {\"ngram\": \"a QR code\", \"from\": 5666, \"to\": 5675}, {\"ngram\": \"a walk\", \"from\": 5686, \"to\": 5692}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"a hit\", \"from\": 5750, \"to\": 5755}, {\"ngram\": \"some Parisians\", \"from\": 5761, \"to\": 5775}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 5780, \"to\": 5788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision by the Paris transport authority to hike fares on the M\\u00e9tro from \\u20ac2.15 (\\u00a31.81) for a single journey to \\u20ac4 (\\u00a33.36) for the duration of the Games is just one hindrance among several that have rubbed the citizens of the City of Light up the wrong way.\", \"from\": 5797, \"to\": 6058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5817, \"end\": 5822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.075874275631171e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 5797, \"to\": 5809}, {\"ngram\": \"fares\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5856}, {\"ngram\": \"the M\\u00e9tro\", \"from\": 5860, \"to\": 5869}, {\"ngram\": \"a single journey\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 5909}, {\"ngram\": \"the duration\", \"from\": 5928, \"to\": 5940}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5944, \"to\": 5953}, {\"ngram\": \"just one hindrance\", \"from\": 5957, \"to\": 5975}, {\"ngram\": \"the citizens\", \"from\": 6007, \"to\": 6019}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 6023, \"to\": 6031}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 6035, \"to\": 6040}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong way\", \"from\": 6044, \"to\": 6057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games Pass, an electronic authorisation required for residents and visitors alike to enter a sprawling zone around the banks of the Seine for the next week ahead of the opening ceremony on 26 July, has led to grumbles that it will drive tourists away and impede Parisians going about their daily business.\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6196, \"end\": 6201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9573886090615595e-22, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Games Pass\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6074}, {\"ngram\": \"an electronic authorisation\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6103}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 6117, \"to\": 6126}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 6131, \"to\": 6139}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprawling zone\", \"from\": 6155, \"to\": 6171}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 6179, \"to\": 6188}, {\"ngram\": \"the next week\", \"from\": 6206, \"to\": 6219}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 6229, \"to\": 6249}, {\"ngram\": \"26 July\", \"from\": 6253, \"to\": 6260}, {\"ngram\": \"grumbles\", \"from\": 6273, \"to\": 6281}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 6301, \"to\": 6309}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 6326, \"to\": 6335}, {\"ngram\": \"their daily business\", \"from\": 6348, \"to\": 6368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One TikTok video by a French-American creator urging people to stay away from Paris during the Games - \\\"Do not come, cancel everything\\\" - has now garnered more than 760,000 views.\", \"from\": 6371, \"to\": 6550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6375, \"end\": 6381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.946858055549941e-57, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 6449, \"end\": 6454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.075874275631171e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a French-American creator\", \"from\": 6391, \"to\": 6416}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6424, \"to\": 6430}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6471}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 6495, \"to\": 6505}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 760,000 views\", \"from\": 6526, \"to\": 6549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are increasing concerns that many have heeded such advice.\", \"from\": 6552, \"to\": 6616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 6573, \"to\": 6581}, {\"ngram\": \"such advice\", \"from\": 6604, \"to\": 6615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a spike in hotel prices, room rates have fallen dramatically from \\u20ac523 (\\u00a3440) to \\u20ac282 (\\u00a3237) a night for a three-star room during the Games, and \\u20ac738 (\\u00a3621) to \\u20ac430 (\\u00a3362) for four-star lodgings.\", \"from\": 6617, \"to\": 6818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spike\", \"from\": 6623, \"to\": 6630}, {\"ngram\": \"hotel prices\", \"from\": 6634, \"to\": 6646}, {\"ngram\": \"room rates\", \"from\": 6648, \"to\": 6658}, {\"ngram\": \"a three-star room\", \"from\": 6728, \"to\": 6745}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6753, \"to\": 6762}, {\"ngram\": \"four-star lodgings\", \"from\": 6799, \"to\": 6817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Air France-KLM has reported a dip in revenues of \\u20ac180m (\\u00a3151) for July and August with large numbers of seats unsold.\", \"from\": 6820, \"to\": 6948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6831, \"end\": 6845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\\u2013KLM\", \"score\": 0.9999965368902788, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Air France-KLM\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\\u2013KLM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\\u2013KLM\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dip\", \"from\": 6859, \"to\": 6864}, {\"ngram\": \"revenues\", \"from\": 6868, \"to\": 6876}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 6897, \"to\": 6901}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 6906, \"to\": 6912}, {\"ngram\": \"large numbers\", \"from\": 6918, \"to\": 6931}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 6935, \"to\": 6940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Galeries Lafayette, a landmark Parisian department store, has said it expects its revenues to be down by 10 per cent for August.\", \"from\": 6949, \"to\": 7077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Galeries Lafayette\", \"from\": 6949, \"to\": 6967}, {\"ngram\": \"a landmark Parisian department store\", \"from\": 6969, \"to\": 7005}, {\"ngram\": \"its revenues\", \"from\": 7027, \"to\": 7039}, {\"ngram\": \"10 per cent\", \"from\": 7054, \"to\": 7065}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 7070, \"to\": 7076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, London experienced a similar drop in tourism numbers during the 2012 Olympics and the Paris authorities insist a good time will be had by those who come to - or remain in - the French capital.\", \"from\": 7079, \"to\": 7282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7090, \"end\": 7096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999763531, \"rank\": 2.33126454317484e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 7176, \"end\": 7181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.075874275631171e-33, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 7267, \"end\": 7273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9969834902429977, \"rank\": 0.0025021586657926103, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a similar drop\", \"from\": 7109, \"to\": 7123}, {\"ngram\": \"tourism numbers\", \"from\": 7127, \"to\": 7142}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 Olympics\", \"from\": 7150, \"to\": 7167}, {\"ngram\": \"a good time\", \"from\": 7201, \"to\": 7212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As one local organising committee official put it recently: \\\"It's going to be magic.\\\"\", \"from\": 7284, \"to\": 7369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one local organising committee official\", \"from\": 7287, \"to\": 7326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps unsurprisingly, the watchword for those involved with ensuring security at the Games is therefore vigilance.\", \"from\": 7371, \"to\": 7487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the watchword\", \"from\": 7395, \"to\": 7408}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 7442, \"to\": 7450}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7454, \"to\": 7463}, {\"ngram\": \"vigilance\", \"from\": 7477, \"to\": 7486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB, which is sending 327 athletes to the Games to compete in 24 sports, will be protected by a security team of private contractors, many of them former Metropolitan Police Service close protection officers, who liaise closely with both the French and UK authorities.\", \"from\": 7489, \"to\": 7761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7489, \"end\": 7496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.8798876929262734, \"rank\": 0.13650854530222273, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 7735, \"end\": 7741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9969834902429977, \"rank\": 0.0025021586657926103, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 7746, \"end\": 7748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2803329283095655e-17, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"327 athletes\", \"from\": 7515, \"to\": 7527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7531, \"to\": 7540}, {\"ngram\": \"24 sports\", \"from\": 7555, \"to\": 7564}, {\"ngram\": \"a security team\", \"from\": 7587, \"to\": 7602}, {\"ngram\": \"private contractors\", \"from\": 7606, \"to\": 7625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is understood that no threat specific to the British team has been identified.\", \"from\": 7762, \"to\": 7843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7810, \"end\": 7817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999818101, \"rank\": 1.8194259875138797e-11, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no threat\", \"from\": 7784, \"to\": 7793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British Olympic Association said it had \\\"complete confidence\\\" in the ability of the French authorities and the Games' organisers to provide a safe environment for both athletes and fans.\", \"from\": 7845, \"to\": 8035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7849, \"end\": 7876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 7933, \"end\": 7939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc